videos.description: Missouri's Terrence Phillips hits a beautiful spin move to dish the ball to Cullen VanLeer, who sinks an easy 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: Missouri's Phillips' drive and dish leads to 3-pointer
Mizzou freshman throws down thunderous slam

videos.description: Missouri's zone defense is no match for Arizona's Kobi Simmons as he charges the lane to lay in the ball.
videos.headline: Arizona's Simmons splits the D and shows the soft touch

videos.description: Arizona's Kobi Simmons capitalizes on the Wildcats' 14-0 run with a corner 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Simmons' corner 3-pointer gives Arizona largest lead of game
